 Visual Description
The game features:

Classic green felt table background

Blue card backs with gold diamond pattern

Clear card faces with suits and ranks

Red and black suit colors

Organized layout with stock, waste, foundations, and 7 tableau columns

 Game Rules
Tableau: Build descending sequences alternating colors (red/black)

Foundations: Build ascending sequences by suit (Ace to King)

Stock: Draw 3 cards at a time

Waste: Top card can be moved to tableau or foundation

Empty tableau columns: Can only be filled with a King

 Customization Options
You can easily customize:

Colors: Modify constants.py

Card size: Change CARD_WIDTH and CARD_HEIGHT

Layout: Adjust LEFT_OFFSET, TOP_OFFSET, etc.

